courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, B2, C1, C2, C4, D1, D2, D3, and D4. C4 should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). Refer to online catalog for GE course selection, USCP and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR). USCP requirement can be satisfied by some (but not all) courses within GE categories: C4, D1, D3, or D4.
